data.description: YOUR SEARCH STOPS HERE! This 3,458 square foot contemporary home encases a potential mother in law suit, tasteful modern updates, and a screened back porch. Sitting on over five acres of waterfront property located in one of the most well desired locations in Florida with a 25x45 detached garage, two additional carports, and two utility buildings. This fully fenced serene hammock land is bountiful with mature palm trees, live oaks, pines, cabbage palms, and other native vegetation. Property adjoins the Orange State Canal leading directly to the Withlacoochee River and Tsala Apopa Chains. Drop the boat in the water and head over to Stumpknockers and treat yourself to some great seafood. What more could you ask for? This incredible deal checks all the boxes, so don’t wait. This deal will go faster than a toupee in a hurricane. Inquire today!
